    <stitle>POWER STEERING GEAR: SHEPPARD M-SERIES - STEERING SYSTEM DIAGNOSIS - DEFINE THE COMPLAINT</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="diagnose" graphiccount="0">
        <title>DEFINE THE COMPLAINT</title>
        <seqlist>
            <item>
                <para>Talk to and question the driver. Refer to the
                    <hotlnk document="s05002y_HL0500201.xml" xrefid="hl0500201">GLOSSARY OF TERMS AND DEFINITIONS
                    </hotlnk>
                    to obtain a clear understanding of what the driver is saying.
                </para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>Drive the vehicle. If possible, have the driver show you what he is experiencing. Drive the
                    vehicle together to duplicate the condition.
                </para>
            </item>
        </seqlist>
    </svcproc>
